SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations (Pilot Project No. 22)
PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS (PILOT PROJECT NO. 22) in order to introduce a pilot project that provides up to four additional weeks of EI regular benefits to seasonal claimants whose benefit period is established between September 10, 2023 and September 7, 2024.
